data.description: ASSUMABLE 3.8% FHA LOAN!Escape to the tranquility of country living in this foundation strong modular home, set on over 10 acres of scenic beauty. With 2400 sqft of living space. This residence offers the perfect blend of comfort and charm.Step through the front door into a spacious interior and open floor plan that includes not only 3 bedrooms and 2 full baths, but also a dedicated office space that could be used for a 4th bedroom, work or relaxation. The heart of the home features a cozy pellet insert fireplace, creating a warm and inviting atmosphere during cooler seasons.This chef's delight kitchen boasts a huge island for all your meal prepping needs. Step out back to a massive covered deck, providing an ideal spot for dining or taking in the breathtaking views of the countryside. The property has a wealth of practical features, including a one year old HVAC unit for year round comfort. Rest easy knowing the modular home is securely anchored to a foundation with hurricane tie-down straps, ensuring stability and peace of mind in any weather. You can have comfort in knowing you have many years left with the roof that is only six years old.For the avid DIY enthusiast, the expansive 30x38 attached garage with a workbench and the additional 20x30 detached shop provide ample space for projects and storage.There is an incomplete 6'x4' Concrete storm shelter in the attached garage with 12'' thick concrete. It would not take much for a new homeowner to complete the shelter.But there's more... the property owner states that multiple wild deer graze the grounds daily, adding a touch of nature's beauty to your everyday life.Don't miss this opportunity to own a country retreat with all the bells and whistles. Contact us today to schedule a private showing and make this your dream home!
